description:
Jewel Match is a funny line match game where you match all the same obstacles in a line to remove them and let the jewel hit the dotted line. The simple line match mechanic and plenty of variety keeps the game interesting and fun for all ages!
Get all jewels in Jewel Match!

Features:
- 50 Levels
- Simple line three match mechanic
- A variety of levels
name: Jewel Match
